          <span>Current Liabilities</span><span>$80M</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bs-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f97316,#ea6a0e);height:20%" title="Long-term Debt: $60M">
          <span>Long-term Debt</span><span>$60M</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bs-bar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#10b981,#0d9668);height:53%" title="Shareholders' Equity: $160M">
