      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══ SAMPLE BALANCE SHEET ═══ -->
    <h2 id="balance-sheet-example">Balance Sheet Example: TechCorp Inc.</h2>
    <p>Below is a sample balance sheet for the fictional <strong>TechCorp Inc.</strong> as of December 31, 2025. All figures are in millions (USD).</p>

    <div class="sample-bs">
      <div class="sample-bs-header">TechCorp Inc. — Consolidated Balance Sheet</div>
      <div class="sample-bs-sub">As of December 31, 2025 (in millions USD)</div>
